sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthServer as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Backend as odh-dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant MRBFF as model-registry-ui BFF<br/>8043/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant ModelRegistry as Model Registry API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Upstream as Upstream Services<br/>(Pipelines, TrustyAI, etc.)
    participant Thanos as Thanos/Prometheus<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Browser, K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Dashboard Access
        Browser->>Route: GET / (HTTPS/443, TLS edge)
        Route->>OAuthProxy: Forward (HTTPS/8443, TLS reencrypt)
        OAuthProxy-->>Browser: 302 Redirect to OAuth
        Browser->>OAuthServer: OpenShift credentials (HTTPS/443)
        OAuthServer-->>Browser: OAuth session cookie
        Browser->>Route: GET / + OAuth cookie
        Route->>OAuthProxy: Forward with cookie
        OAuthProxy->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token header
        Backend->>K8sAPI: GET /api/v1/users/~ (HTTPS/443, Bearer Token)
        K8sAPI-->>Backend: User identity + admin status
        Backend-->>OAuthProxy: Dashboard HTML + config
        OAuthProxy-->>Route: HTTPS response
        Route-->>Browser: Dashboard UI
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Browser, ModelRegistry: Flow 2: Model Registry Operations (via BFF sidecar)
        Browser->>Route: POST /_mf/modelRegistry/api/v1/... (HTTPS/443)
        Route->>OAuthProxy: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
        OAuthProxy->>Backend: HTTP/8080, x-forwarded-access-token
        Backend->>MRBFF: Proxy to HTTPS/8043<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
        MRBFF->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview (SAR check)<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>MRBFF: SAR result (allowed/denied)
        MRBFF->>ModelRegistry: GET/POST /api/model_registry/...<br/>HTTP/8080, Bearer Token
        ModelRegistry-->>MRBFF: Model data (JSON)
        MRBFF-->>Backend: Response
        Backend-->>OAuthProxy: Response
        OAuthProxy-->>Browser: Model Registry data
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Browser, K8sAPI: Flow 3: Notebook Lifecycle Management
        Browser->>Route: POST /api/notebooks/:ns/:name (HTTPS/443)
        Route->>OAuthProxy: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
        OAuthProxy->>Backend: HTTP/8080, x-forwarded-access-token
        Backend->>K8sAPI: Create/Patch Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (user)
        K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook CR status
        Backend->>K8sAPI: GET Pod status<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (SA)
        K8sAPI-->>Backend: Pod running status
        Backend-->>Browser: Notebook status response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over Browser, Upstream: Flow 4: Service Proxy (Pipelines, TrustyAI, etc.)
        Browser->>Route: GET /api/service/pipelines/:ns/:name/* (HTTPS/443)
        Route->>OAuthProxy: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
        OAuthProxy->>Backend: HTTP/8080, x-forwarded-access-token
        Backend->>K8sAPI: Lookup gating resource<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (SA)
        K8sAPI-->>Backend: Service endpoint info
        Backend->>Upstream: Proxy request<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token (user)
        Upstream-->>Backend: Service response
        Backend-->>Browser: Proxied response
    end
